Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花真的很好看  谢谢你们把我叫来
