Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.21,0:00:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小聪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.59,0:00:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那我就先…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  路上慢点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  来接我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}爸爸  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.85,0:01:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.03,0:01:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.55,0:01:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜呢  可能愿望不是这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,0:01:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  芽间有些幸运哦  电视上最近放的Dodosuko我很喜欢
